            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The school is doing excellent in all the fields especially giving a lot of exposure to children. Good efforts by all the teachers. I am very grateful to all teachers, HMs and HODs. They are approachable.  My child is being groomed very well. Various Co-Curricular activities are organized by the school which helps a child to develop confidence and overcome stage fear. Keep it up! I wish great success to Gaurs International School.",
