            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The academic programs at Gaurs International School are well-structured and diverse. The curriculum is engaging, offering a good balance between core subjects and electives.\nThe teachers demonstrate a strong commitment to student success, providing support and encouragement.The teaching staff at is knowledgeable and passionate about their subjects. They go beyond the curriculum to foster a positive learning environment.\nI appreciate the accessibility of teachers for additional assistance when needed.The school's facilities are well-maintained and conducive to learning. The classrooms are equipped with modern technology, and the library provides a resourceful space for research. One of the highlights is its vibrant extracurricular scene. From sports to arts and cultural activities, there is something for everyone. These activities contribute significantly to the holistic development of students. The overall atmosphere at GIS is inclusive and friendly. Students are encouraged to express themselves, fostering a sense of community. The school promotes diversity and embraces different perspectives.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
